FBIS4-41410 "drsov122_b_94023" FBIS-SOV-94-122 Daily Report 23 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Soskovets Raps Fuel Ministry Forecasts Soskovets Raps Fuel Ministry Forecasts LD2306140394 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 23 Jun 94 LD2306140394 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] At today's meeting of the cabinet, Oleg Soskovets, Russian first deputy prime minister, voiced his dissatisfaction with the Ministry of Fuel and Power Engineering's position while discussing the issue of how enterprises and organizations were preparing for the fall and winter period. According to him, the panic-stricken pronouncements by the ministry's representative to the effect that we will not survive this winter can mean only one thing: Such people should be found who will be able to organize work in a new way.
